Question2 
Main path and alternate path of one use case
   --> Use case <Setting username and password>

1.User wants to register the online UNO game.
2.User is required to enter desired name.
3.User is required to set password.
    3.1 User enter desired password having 8 or more characters and
        containing more than a special character.
    3.2 User enter desired password which is less than 8 letters or without any special character.
3.2.2 User see the requirements for password and is asked to enter again until user enter password fulfilling the requirement.
4.User see the message "New User Added," his/her username.  